Top performers:
- "Carving a 🦆out of Wood & Epoxy" (2.0x, BM Sculptures)\n- "Carving a Figure out of Epoxy & Wood" (2.0x, BM Sculptures)\n- "Carving wood & epoxy into a 🦏" (2.0x, BM Sculptures)\n- "Carving a 🐢 out of Epoxy & Wood" (1.9x, BM Sculptures)
